Cycle reference point: End of cycle
Analysis classes: Year, Difference between predicted and achieved BTEC Extended diploma points, Reformed BTEC indicator, Ethnic group, Applicant type

Coverage: UK, 18 year old, main scheme applicants with a predicted BTEC Extended diploma. Restricted to applicants where the reformed/non-reformed status of their predicted and achieved BTEC extended diplomas is the same.
Technical notes and definitions available on ucas.com.
